
    The cops in Westenburg, Polokwane in Limpopo have arrested a fake
police officer.The 25-year-old man is believed to be amongst the people
who are terrorizing members of the community while posing as police. According to the police spokesperson Colonel Moetshe
Ngeope the suspect was arrested after he and his accomplice gave their victim a
